channel.title: The overall quality of this place has lowered
channel.description:
If I wanted to read an inteligent debate about something I always had this forum in reserve. I never did contribute myself all that much but when I didn't post I could see how I could improve on my previous errors based on everypost around me. Since the release of new info I've noticed a steady decline in the high-quality this place once had.
I guess I'm probably over exaggerating a bit much, but a month before the facebook release I could "lurk" here and still learn from every other post. Its only gotten much worse since the youtube video was leaked. I guess it is to be expected as only the veterans really stayed here while the BM team were dark but it is still unfortunate when I look back on it.
This thread's discussion value is how the new people here because of the leaked footage are annoying.
